<h2 id="toc2"><span>附录5982.2</span></h2>
<h3 id="toc3"><span><tt>布道摘录</tt></span></h3>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▶展开附录◀</a></div>
